Class ScriptBasedOIDCProtocolMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.keycloak.protocol.oidc.mappers.AbstractOIDCProtocolMapper
      • org.keycloak.protocol.oidc.mappers.ScriptBasedOIDCProtocolMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIDCAccessTokenMapper, OIDCIDTokenMapper, UserInfoTokenMapper, ProtocolMapper, ConfiguredProvider, Provider, ProviderFactory<ProtocolMapper>

    public class ScriptBasedOIDCProtocolMapper
extends AbstractOIDCProtocolMapper
implements OIDCAccessTokenMapper, OIDCIDTokenMapper, UserInfoTokenMapper
    OIDC ProtocolMapper that uses a provided JavaScript fragment to compute the token claim value.
